## Frequently Asked Questions

### **What happens during a typical intake session at Riaz Counseling?**

Your initial session is a collaborative clinical assessment. Your therapist at **Riaz Counseling** will explore your current challenges, gather relevant historical background, and work alongside you to map out clear, attainable goals for your mental wellness journey.

### **Is virtual counseling as effective as traditional in-person therapy?**

Yes. Extensive clinical research confirms that secure, HIPAA-compliant telehealth yields identical therapeutic outcomes to traditional in-person care for a wide range of struggles, including generalized anxiety, depression, lifestyle transitions, and stress management.

